title: European and American Paintings in the I. S. Gardner Museum
description:
European and American Paintings in the Isabella Stewart Gardner Museum

IS Gardner Museum | 1974 | ISBN 0914660004 | Eng | 378 pages | PDF | 48.5 MB

This second catalogue of all the exhibited European and American paintings in the Gardner Museum continues the tradition of scholarship, generously framed with personal insights, which was established by Sir Philip Hendy in the first catalogue printed in 1931. A new format allows for a longer text, an illustration of each of the 282 paintings in the collection, and 38 color plates
